  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK872">
<l>villē ruḻavar pakaikoḷiṉuṅ koḷḷaṟka</l>
<l>collē ruḻavar pakai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Though you may incur the hatred of warriors whose ploughs are bows, incur not that of ministers whose ploughs are words.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
